name: Christopher_Knight_Home_Outdoor_Antibes_3-piece_Wicker_Bistro_Set_with_Cushions
reviews: I like the chairs! I haven't been able to put them with the table yet, but I like Christopher Knight products! They are great for the money! They hold up really well and are very comfortable.

The orders was shipped on time and arrived at our villa several days early. The packaging was excellent. The assembly instructions were very clear and the estimated assemble time was accurate. Once assembled (less than 30 minutes per chair), the items were substantial, solid, comfortable. So far, I would recommend.
description: Charming and attractive, this Christopher Knight Home Antibes 3-piece wicker bistro set will add a comfortable refinement to your patio or outdoor setting. The accent table and soft chairs are durable and weather resistant.
